msg":"下次會唔會玩茶樓點心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ede05d5fd58cfb2b903b1cc0686518ce1bdf8c","tid":394762,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"反正都犯法，做乜唔直接屌？"},{"pid":"c09abcecd3a83d121fdee90ef7c477fa3f1809a6","tid":394762,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d無確切證據都有得咁判<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n甲○於傳送上開訊息予丁○○時，既無法預料該訊息紀錄將供日後證據之用，應無故意設計對話或有其他虛偽之可能。益徵甲○於偵訊、本院審理時之上開證述內容，應為可採<br />\n<br />\n本身無諗住報警 LINE有求醫既對話 時間上吻合 <br />\n判決主文有得睇<br />\n<br />\n詳情 : 臺灣臺中地方法院刑事判決 106年度侵訴字第2號"},{"pid":"7f58daedcab8ba8626d74cfbca8a3d1ff67a0209","tid":394762,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"因此仍依強制性交罪將他判刑3年6月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃瓜插閪都當性交?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cf44f1b2279fc878d2b7436cd25d4a6a41861e","tid":394762,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"條黃瓜係咪有刺個種"}]}